  <Series>Judge Dredd: Brothers of the Blood</Series>
  <Summary>After sentencing Gladys Ecks to eighteen months' imprisonment for welfare fraud and shoplifting, Judge Dredd recalls his intention to watch his niece, Vienna Pasternak (whose parents he killed when she was a small child), perform in a play - 'Charles III' - at The Megalopolis theatre. Although he requests three hours of downtime to see the play, he ends up using it to assist two judges pinned down by a rogue citidef (city defense) unit and arrives too late at the theatre to catch up with Vienna. His downtime up, he proceeds to his next case.

Judge Rico survives shoot-out but remains a pariah with his fellow judges in Tac Group 9. The leak in the group is also discovered.

Judge Dredd does not appear in this story.</Summary>
